                      Recent Activity
                      {!searchTerm && <span className="text-xs bg-white border border-gray-200 text-gray-400 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md font-normal">Last 10</span>}
                  </h3>
                   <div className="relative w-full md:w-72">
